@host = http://localhost:5000

### Health check
GET {{host}}/

### Create a trade
# @name createTrade
POST {{host}}/api/trades
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "instrument": "USDCAD",
  "quantity": 1000000,
  "side": "Buy"
}

### Fetch the trade we just created
GET {{host}}/api/trades/{{createTrade.response.body.id}}

### Price it
POST {{host}}/api/trades/{{createTrade.response.body.id}}/price
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 1.37,
  "currency": "CAD"
}

### Execute it
POST {{host}}/api/trades/{{createTrade.response.body.id}}/execute
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "executionPrice": 1.371,
  "counterparty": "BankX"
}

### Try to cancel after execution — should 422 (business rule violation)
POST {{host}}/api/trades/{{createTrade.response.body.id}}/cancel
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "too late"
}

### Amend a (different) trade before pricing
# @name createAmendable
POST {{host}}/api/trades
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "instrument": "EURUSD",
  "quantity": 500000,
  "side": "Sell"
}

### Amend its quantity
POST {{host}}/api/trades/{{createAmendable.response.body.id}}/amend
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "newQuantity": 750000
}

### Cancel it
POST {{host}}/api/trades/{{createAmendable.response.body.id}}/cancel
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "client withdrew"
}

### Seed — drop 5 trades across every lifecycle state. Useful right after `docker compose up -d`.
POST {{host}}/api/seed

### List all trades (newest first, capped at 100)
GET {{host}}/api/trades

### Filter by status
GET {{host}}/api/trades?status=Priced

### Filter by instrument
GET {{host}}/api/trades?instrument=USDCAD

### Combined filter
GET {{host}}/api/trades?status=Created&instrument=EURUSD

### Daily volume roll-up — rolls up all TradeOrderCreated events by (date, instrument)
GET {{host}}/api/daily-volume

### Error paths
### 400 — zero quantity
POST {{host}}/api/trades
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "instrument": "USDCAD",
  "quantity": 0,
  "side": "Buy"
}

### 404 — unknown id
GET {{host}}/api/trades/aaaaaaaa-bbbb-cccc-dddd-eeeeeeeeeeee
